msgid "Use a Team Project"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:4
msgid ""
"OmegaT team projects must first be `set up <#howto.setupteamproject>`__ "
"on a server."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:7
msgid ""
"To use a team project for the first time, follow the procedure provided "
"by the project manager."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:10
msgid ""
"Once the project has been opened, translation proceeds in the same way as"
" for a non-team project, except the following points."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:13
msgid "**Automatic saving**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:15
msgid ""
"Every 3 minutes (by default), the local project is synchronised with the "
"remote repository so that the project manager or other translators can "
"see and use translations added during that period."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:19
msgid ""
"The interval of 3 minutes can be changed in `Options > Preferences > "
"Saving and Output <#dialogs.preferences.savingandoutput>`__."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:22
msgid "**Synchronised files**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:24
msgid ""
"Whenever the project is automatically saved, but also when it is opened, "
"closed and reloaded, only two files are actually synchronised:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:27
msgid "``omegat/project_save.tmx``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:29
msgid "``glossary/glossary.txt``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:31
msgid "All other files will be replaced by the files in the remote repository."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:33
msgid "**Adding new source files**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:35
msgid "To add a new source file:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:37
msgid "copy the files to the ``/source`` folder"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:39
msgid "use Project > Commit Source Files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:41
msgid ""
"Existing source files can be modified, but the commit operation must be "
"carried out before an automatic save and before the project is reloaded "
"or closed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:45
msgid "**Deleting source files**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:47
msgid "Files must be deleted first by the project manager, and then locally."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:49
msgid "**Changing segmentation rules or file filters**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:51
msgid "Project parameters must be changed by the project manager."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:53
msgid "**Working offline**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:55
msgid ""
"A team project can be opened and translated offline. All the changes will"
" be synchronised the next time a connection is available."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:58
msgid "To work offline:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/HowTo_UseTeamProject.rst:60
msgid "Disconnect from the network before opening the project,"
msgstr ""

